			</td>		</tr>	</tbody></table><p>注：毕业论文是该项目的旗舰课程，学生不但可以选择自己感兴趣的研究方向进一步研究还可为就业做准备*(2)</p><p><strong>国际旅游与酒店管理硕士（MSc International Tourism and Hospitality Management</strong><strong>）：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width:100%">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="height:18px; width:14.58%">			<p>课程名称</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:15.4%">			<p>课程英文名</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:26.24%">			<p>课程名称</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:43.78%">			<p>课程英文名</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="height:18px; width:14.58%">			<p>人力管理</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:15.4%">			<p>Managing People</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:26.24%">			<p>就业实习项目</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:43.78%">			<p>Work Based Project</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="height:18px; width:14.58%">			<p>研究理论</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:15.4%">			<p>Research Methods</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:26.24%">			<p>酒店<a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/社会学' target='_blank'>社会学</a>与经济学框架</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:43.78%">			<p>Hospitality <a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/社会学' target='_blank'>Sociology</a> and Economic Framework</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="height:18px; width:14.58%">			<p>市场营销</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:15.4%">			<p>Marketing</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:26.24%">			<p>毕业论文</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:43.78%">			<p>Dissertation</p>			</td>		</tr>	</tbody></table><p>*(3)</p><p><strong>管理学研究硕士（MRes Management</strong><strong>）：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width:100.0%">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="height:18px; width:13.94%">			<p>课程名称</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:40.14%">			<p>课程英文名</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:10.06%">			<p>课程名称</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:35.84%">			<p>课程英文名</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td st