4.76%">			<p>Research Methods</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="height:18px; width:20.96%">			<p>数字经济学与新商业建模</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:40.92%">			<p>New Business Models for the Digital Economy</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:13.36%">			<p>毕业论文</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:24.76%">			<p>Dissertation</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="height:18px; width:20.96%">			<p>数字市场</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:40.92%">			<p>Digital Marketing</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:13.36%">&nbsp;</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:24.76%">&nbsp;</td>		</tr>	</tbody></table><p>*(5)</p><p><strong>研究设置</strong></p><p>管理学研究型项目（包括旅游管理）（MPhil/PhD Management (including Tourism)）开设的研究领域有：</p><ul>	<li>成功人士讲述游戏领先规则（The tales top bosses tell to keep ahead of the game）</li>	<li>微商运营战略（Operations and strategy in micro-businesses）</li>	<li>发展中国家环境与矛盾战略（Strategy in conflict and developing country environments）</li>	<li>有效商业战略（Effective business strategies）</li>	<li>经济服务化与发展（&lsquo;Servitization&rsquo; and how to develop it）</li>	<li>市场与社会背景（The social context of markets）</li>	<li>会展管理（Events management）</li>	<li>小型企业与管理创新（Small businesses and entrepreneurship）</li>	<li>学习与发现（How can we engage people in learning and discovery?）</li>	<li>就业质量与多样化（Workplace equality / diversity）</li>	<li>组织启示（Organisational storytelling）</li>	<li>风险资本与高科技年轻企业（Venture capital and high tech young firms）</li>	<li>创新过程（The process of innovation）</li>	<li>零售与创新（Retail innovation）</li>	<li>旅游、超市与凯德伯里家族（Tourism, supermarkets, faith-based institutions and Cadburys）*(6)</li></ul><p>领导力研究型项目（MPhil/PhD Leadership）开设的研究领域及中心有：</p><ul>	<li>领导力研究中心（Centre for Leadership Studies (CLS)）</li>	<li>最新研究：非正式领导力对学术化影响更深（Informal leadership more influential for academics says new research）</li>	<li>领先公司：企业领导持续研究（Leading FTSE companies: a continuing study of corporate directing）</li>	<li>性别与管理岗位的关系（The gender pay gap in managerial positions）</li>	<li>领导力与商业管理概念的关系（&ldquo;Leadership is one of the most talked about yet misunderstood concepts in business and management&rdquo;）</li>	<li>我们如何采取有效措施和领导力应对天气变化（How can we develop leadership and procurement skills for climate change?）</li>	<li>领导力与道德、创新及改革的关系（Leadership &ndash; relating to ethics, innovation and change）</li>	<li>如何进行团队工作（How do teams &lsquo;do teamwork&rsquo;?）*(7)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>管理学专业项目列表：<a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=2rNMmQ1swUvq6KgRlllllluyWqQeKE6x625K5K40S1F0l3MqxHBbNf_CN2E9MuTwZuZ-VN9ueNdu4zuXvY78725fpPWf5_7VviTDB3n' target='_blank'>Postgraduate Degrees</a></li>	<li>管理学专业导师列表：<a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=lreSUwjZw9P-F3uvyyyyyjU24ViGWO6zCbgGCBTxYrHzYrJ29f6SvZBk9AixYETP5uTN5dR0rfv0yNY0-JUVrNvs6fUFy5P06fnFriC8fkCtp8o1j8xqV6VfpkCqp3C8fkCtp8oD' target='_blank'>Staff in Management</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=2rNMmQniLOJkATOk3rb7mthIZg_-vF3hqrcJLo_tqtzis8gZ1hm0JJf3D2t5ZQ7bANKa5jMi0Pl1-VAiU5_pRSTsj3kTG8w0Ipjqx_Y-B7qxi1gh-BWi_iH1OtlaVWB7ZBrkoUK-4bd-LAl_wT7WancIX0CqOwvdq05xIYhs3JHf8uGhse' target='_blank'>MSc International Management</a> University of Exeter</p><p>(2) <a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=BraKR4sTLNk2Bl-7OOOOONEbqCDMsjlK7ahlhlA91g5Ejx3ClbzTNdFoNiPdUSauHSHh0LP23Lw2mPCDZEe0eJCXHBxXgjngOZjXMrtvoZadCGYK9ahmKS6ckg_RmgifmDM5txnAlD3Q7aAsWwj4A8DWKqPQMKHaXJlbWVuahnb' target='_blank'>MSc International Tourism Management</a> University of Exeter</p><p>(3) <a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=6ri8vermwnkBwWYSrrrrr9WxRolh0mnyefjqjqGo1cWU-aLCMSNVBsduBM-YW5ZlP5PtK7t1B7S1UTL3RhdWdof5ruH54Z-5tHJOXSPDoQGhDgtz4H_hXDNiyQoLSlpgt3eDRoe0Ksbo9qIL-yavLxRDdkNQB4tQIk' target='_blank'>MSc International Tourism and Hospitality Management</a> University of Exeter</p><p>(4) <a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=hrfXwi00wI0Gi4qHooooot1H3TC9NPaDZ7v9v9buwMwfyX1PcU3iqmQwqk2-6mQ-DmD9H-FCc-_CAZ7vB69M9KD-z8Z-xeOQoupafz-l6Eg0ZiQzjeO7oyXLi1rzPyWilB7vebtJe3HYnmn3Xlnj3VvzuD' t