论文（研究生文凭课程无需撰写毕业论文）。非欧盟国际学生可以申请研究生<a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/奖学金' target='_blank'>奖学金</a>，具体见研究生申请说明。*(1)</li></ul><p><strong>课程设置</strong></p><p>埃克塞特大学人力资源管理项目研究生开设的核心必修课程包括：</p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width:100%">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="height:18px; width:14.16%">			<p>课程名称</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:32.28%">			<p>课程英文名</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:14.72%">			<p>课程名称</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:38.84%">			<p>课程英文名</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="height:18px; width:14.16%">			<p>人力领导、管理与开发</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:32.28%">			<p>Leading, Managing and Developing People [Both PGDip &amp; MSc]</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:14.72%">			<p>国际人力资源管理</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:38.84%">			<p>International Human Resource Management [OR BEMM046 for both PGDip &amp; MSc]</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="height:18px; width:14.16%">			<p>资源与人才管理</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:32.28%">			<p>Resourcing and Talent Management [Both PGDip &amp; MSc]</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:14.72%">			<p>人力资源技能</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:38.84%">			<p>HR Skills [Both PGDip &amp; MSc]</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="height:18px; width:14.16%">			<p>人力资源管理与环境</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:32.28%">			<p>Human Resource Management in Context [Both PGDip &amp; MSc]</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:14.72%">			<p>管理研究项目</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:38.84%">			<p>Management Research Report [PGDip Only]</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="height:18px; width:14.16%">			<p>人力资源开发</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:32.28%">			<p>Human Resource Development (HRD) [Both PGDip &amp; MSc]</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:14.72%">			<p>研究方法</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:38.84%">			<p>Research Methods [MSc Only]</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td s