与活性材料、负热膨胀材料、聚合物、复合物及生物材料等。非欧盟国际学生可以申请研究生奖学金，具体见研究生申请说明*(2)</li></ul><p><strong>课程设置</strong></p><p>埃克塞特大学材料工程专业开设的核心必修课程有：</p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width:100.0%">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="height:18px; width:40.68%">			<p>课程名称</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:21.36%">			<p>课程英文名</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:13.84%">			<p>课程名称</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:24.12%">			<p>课程英文名</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="height:18px; width:40.68%">			<p>材料力学</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:21.36%">			<p>Mechanics of Materials</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:13.84%">			<p>研究方法</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:24.12%">			<p>Research Methodology</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="height:18px; width:40.68%">			<p>软件建模</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:21.36%">			<p>Software Modelling</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:13.84%">			<p>可持续工程</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:24.12%">			<p>Sustainable Engineering</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="height:18px; width:40.68%">			<p>高级材料工程</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:21.36%">			<p>Advanced Materials Engineering</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:13.84%">			<p>材料工程与新开发</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:24.12%">			<p>New Developments in Materials Engineering</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="height:18px; width:40.68%">			<p>计算机辅助工程设计</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:21.36%">			<p>Computer Aided Engineering Design</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:13.84%">			<p>工程硕士项目</p>			</td>			<td style="height:18px; width:24.12%">			<p>Engineering MSc Project</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td colspan="4" style="height:18px; width:100.0%">			<p><strong>材料工程硕士-</strong><strong>管理学方向（MSc Materials Engineering with Management</strong><strong>）</strong></p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="height:18px; width:40.68%">			<p>材料力学</p>			</td>			<td style="he