ure Mathematics）*(9)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>数学专业项目列表：<a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=yrZqibe1LSONzWapPPPPPPVGSTurogQxR_WdMSQ1T1h-T7Sxcm_RpLdR0x95Fxi2jB2crfFZGLFp4Uip8cdp1Gk1NaHb8afv_n3' target='_blank'>Postgraduate Mathematics</a></li>	<li>数学专业导师列表：<a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=xrVOpgS1wcXfY2U2VVVVVVgTaHR0cDovZ7Aj-iO4aNJRnDu4YFINbMENPkXzuqGY7tYyNxByo9BTEscK3RyJSsDRL0_KAe5kLSoN9U' target='_blank'>Staff Profile</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=DroIGDOpLBGgpjogwwwwwLpcuGurogQxIskWkWjxT0Z2FipK6E8kfL3k1I2r053r3q8kOK8QOhScOi3k3t390x8QOtPkKi3rho2q80iPBPbskMm7Blx2vfIFmPhPQf' target='_blank'>MSc Advanced Mathematics</a> University of Exeter</p><p>(2) <a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=trmo1nTKkgdlWuuF11111Qa82oW4Z0DmGXGXAIJkHMWnw9fsRzfXRrD4H7tXHXAhHFp-HIpxnipf5F5N5Q_AHIpNlF-f5Edtz7jazcCJxfSbMfptEcGr03_q6cGr1oCBETkqtqSv' target='_blank'>MSc Computational Finance</a> University of Exeter</p><p>(3) <a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=orDtO5ZFk2CbM-FnyFxBBI3jkD67SajRIw0DLGlSRqdwA6vq8mEWeLz37WRphtW6I1SPDzP_w16vmMIj5p30PCBAni2m8lR8u5IMhjQCvZ_i2zyWR_r5uCIq-YA-nvw-5h_qfBJnuQR3Ls' target='_blank'>MSc Financial Mathematics</a> University of Exeter</p><p>(4) <a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=rrcuJRvKkgdlWQIqdKhLh0Y2wbwHD1cUDRqkbjZhYiisiivFt_LpJC8IMtU-Ia1gFVhPwlaj5y5G_n_6-tIxU_yF1xBqsiCRSBusUbARqLuclELw3UFT5YpJACHrpacjvMRcrLnO9QgmHE9toLK7UlW9PiXlT_dSHxtICEPy4' target='_blank'>MPhil/PhD Mathematics</a> University of Exeter</p><p>(5) <a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=6ri8veODkbcX2tAGfffffiWu82oW4Z0DvJVeVeIYa9a0B7GJuz549mVh9PG8gY-qyYytgeOcVeycZUAl9I3ja7U31MEAqiIBTAOPTY78yWs2YILljFA3jSAdkPo1xaSZ7rsKNT6GNLhlaI4DwTCUi67CXtB5RCxwQhhwd' target='_blank'>MSc by Research Mathematics</a> University of Exeter</p><p>(6) <a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=7r_i3IKnwmHu4d_N99999N607btTxCNRINV0V0szdSuCqPio6CMCfyLHMtmBhqyKFgyuvVIPbcIwTCBc-bGu4W6KvOS-4ka2y7436Ga5DpxhNPse