 Engineerin</a>g</li>	<li>采矿工程导师列表：<a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=dr1GqVd2kFr4D02KoooooohHmyvZmTDguA79my5Ras4OYK7kufJVwMKfmMnqxN9RxPDEz1hRXND7xPDEz_6oz' target='_blank'>Staff Profile</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=yrZqibeXLCZnSmyMRjd0cy-Wp6KJsJutIvkEgCBDwoBr8xHMOwkS4OmzYT-P6AQrELpaPDkm5SrNrnxo3czkewoB2GxhwFw5O8_shMih9BH9mGj7rUxLm6zT_rJ8UEVzv1aNhQiPTmnSmvY99BYtSusd9UB5ftqN6VAvgraPO' target='_blank'>MSc/PgDip Mining Engineering</a> University of Exeter</p><p>(2) <a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Lr8sWSLcLYq_Z9yXrrrrrJssgkNWw3sgy_T_TcIBdFuWRNJDxzYDTzrgwFSvTFTcxzQnxNQBy_QUTzTsTLSfR6Rx7aNFE1NTIaPWscnTCcRx7aNFE1RTQDny-wREWNK3BuKlFLsH6xSHD6U3qP' target='_blank'>MSc Mining Geology</a> University of Exeter</p><p>(3) <a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=MrO2caiVkPIupgNSsssssgFK9B6sbzYMiLgLgS4zXpnxHy4o9m2u9c2B1rn0fcncgm23am43XtZ3-c2cGcU0Sk2RiFVrSy2RAk2RXMAP-EpM6KpPUXVPU861AwN3w7AT8wp1AE6MW7p3u74viQV8t0R5m4tIlMtLARMuAvtdCHSIOnx' target='_blank'>MSC/PgDip Surveying and Land/Environmental Management</a> University of Exeter</p><p>(4) <a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=urKrNAQhLa4bV7cKsssssI_MCpAbg2K4fqw_w_2FULx3fhkvT8PM0rVe0ozt5KgsqKqkB4SKs4nKNbJbDwkYkl9n8HyF-7rMnsgRaGMlCMpTo5gLntx45r5KqYQX8bq32MAeSCMloUk7AVyeyr4t_vmX1GdXxHNJWuDTPoIvrL-qYLbg-DwaJY9W_i7V' target='_blank'>PgCert Mining Life Cycle</a> University of Exeter</p><p>(5) <a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=xrVOpgSEwgqXDKvP5sBXH8hj4Nb81faBA9ZMNLpSOn6UkFmH7zrWJRtTsO1-zqVfJ2oODYCXFriahQ0shyJNAfizCyl4fXhiu5e_NCQdgG5O40akOjubuv_G2zVoXkhT7cOnuo0e5IDBUIK9zSlt1zSHcXsuyftncgeoPsO253XbFDDdyNYDU82sO25N' target='_blank'>MSc Mining Engineering (Professional)</a> University of Exeter</p><p>(6) <a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=urKrNAS3kCscvoXYjjjOEEW6h_T8SFaCoetetiAmwkH8pV1D9g2Dtg7CM6vWS4v4TB3G8BPGwVn-w6Zud6MUHV3GwAn-wAPfKp3w7_95xHY5BzGREzG5BnK5xHYRDkTsEzGnDmK5xEXsecXnDETslkTsBErzI6HbFUryIo6zm' target='_blank'>MSc by Rese