nergy）：为期4年，属研究型项目，受工程师学会专业认证。要求申请者本科毕业，二类A等荣誉学士学位以上（国内一般要求有硕士学位），拥有相关科学或工程学专业背景，无前置课程要求。需要撰写研究计划，提前联系导师并取得导师的初步录取许可&mdash;&mdash;此为申请成功的关键所在。非欧盟国际学生可以申请IDCORE奖学金，全奖，名额限10名*(2)</li></ul><p><strong>专业设置</strong></p><p>埃克塞特大学可再生能源专业开设的研究领域有：</p><ul>	<li>海洋可再生能源（Offshore renewable energy）</li>	<li>能源储备（Energy storage）</li>	<li>能源政策（Energy policy）</li>	<li>碳捕获与储备（Carbon capture and storage）</li>	<li>电力系统（Electrical power systems）*(5)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>可再生能源专业项目列表：<a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=orDtO5cOwp7How7XDDDmzzzW6CpP_xAMamLB_C3h085bn-LHmaTc7ajLlaWobOTLWI1ot0RXbOTLHi6HYOZx1j8x8K3CrQ3UrfBP' target='_blank'>Postgraduate Renewable Energy</a></li>	<li>可再生能源专业导师列表：<a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=-rGz4Osbw4VCAYQitEMeurf6cyYLnXLFk4iYZnfmh86tTUanTf1Lqqtxiw1zeE-FYyWfHjbqoViRFz55r6Z4jOk-eLOh6Q1Gry4BJFdd6ZRdzDrrFOQRQ' target='_blank'>Staff Profile</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=UrsQlJ6ILgeaoYERdnHSuKrODAFfdRahamGvCCwoawVuB9yp4hedNvnZyc-nVZu1eY0hcdhjAoH6hYBG8sZopt8OrZSeyhrUGNuBgfOSnLcpZ26bSCvRcZ2R7wRmS4wcdQwEXVvC3cphadFfv6qJaLgdhmyy-tWIOZnb1j-UOOjzu3Zqaz' target='_blank'>Masters by Research/MPhil/PhD Renewable Energy</a> University of Exeter</p><p>(2) <a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=YrwF0vrfL_HK0g0SFKEnlIquWJFSdRGhlaX1XxRbr5SA07Fagt_IkHWisptRqUt1rY0q_l8-6tA6-9rBFRfCmhd0jyXOW7wWq-bGPzDaTnVDlYZ6q_K4Y7PAdwXqQHGPMzr7PkHpr8ar7InJEl8ZSqHE0nIvyq7YV4XtOXhnIvyXh6owwT-ITPMM' target='_blank'>EngD Offshore Renewable Energy</a> University of Exeter</p><p>(3) <a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=YrwF0vBlwvLQzIwDikuqGWfvo-SI7o2hyfbuCWJKORHhheeUchnWbOe9rif28_7GaIsOKw6gLeFZdiXWixA8OFe2iD17ITdh4KYYE8lz0srsz1_CFL23ZPGqLh_f9ciCg0B6pqrxP8ohOleuh5Syf23ywGL1RBZygnIm8ohYeSj9CkKz3xefxBzfdeYk4OlrK1pKOV6prAde5Ibxbfch3b3Gi9rsFLnUBPH1a' target='_blank'>Pre-sessional English</a> University of Exeter</p><p>(4) <a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=pr9ExTIWw_8kIp1f9gYZJEBtlrJZkkahn7GH14K8zbSZ