change and sustainable futures）</li>	<li>生态学与保护研究中心（The Centre for Ecology and Conservation）</li>	<li>生物催化中心（The Exeter Biocatalysis Centre）*(9)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>生物科学专业项目列表：<a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=2rNMmQL2kFr4Dfaj1jl1_RUaMXuXdupC4QXxThsJUc6xHrU23C46Nm_UhK_ZUAWVnfvmybwuCd_f37LVKrmmpRVqSy6IUuUUsMz' target='_blank'>Postgraduate Biosciences</a></li>	<li>生物科学专业导师列表：<a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=trmo1nTyk8-j0BcXN93OCnmf7ijsvR63h-Ba949I3odg4Ow___XlBY9dd2Cd0kCFfJERnNQQ19ylRQnm33zc3YGgKWHeSc' target='_blank'>Staff Profile</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=trmo1nqrwMaU29MSuRq2cffH2efpWjlOi4TZwAEmOxhyMjkVjOy9UZPC6UOl5P6jyWmO79bAjU5Ldr34HaPqBF6OGDH5yJfeU3HCkfWBP1rOEKt6z95fagT3Wd6zjpeL4WBPNKOL4S1' target='_blank'>MSc Applied Ecology</a></p><p>(2) <a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Hr3vKzNZw9P-F3ionnnnn_ISJruZ2dOBH8H8KvfXxtu6UWp3Cyp8CFOZx1j8x8K3CrQ3NRXDItXnuBu0u_aO9BaEVfDDxkTDHFa5x1RQSMqsRDqKJdRoAx3GCgpleg_z' target='_blank'>MSc Conservation and Biodiversity</a></p><p>(3)<a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=urKrNASFk2CbMYr-ppppp95Eay1z_Ak5gQgQFZ6lTo1bLnHxK0HQKukzTvWQTQFxKyNxLyV-MvHXPGP2PiRK1GRKYzEcbZFyQnR5EGl8PoKVqriF9zXR_kYn_0G5BL' target='_blank'> MSc Conservation Science and Policy</a></p><p>(4) <a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=yrZqibeBLpMoTsMWLLLLLdECpAbg2K4z6w6wvMecfSbg3ClbeKibIKaNMEtXIEIreK_7eC_SsF_WIKI-Iotk6KtXefSSOZLSMvM1qJR1AJL9gE8lzYuQHBK_q_Le' target='_blank'>MSc Evolutionary and Behavioural Ecology</a></p><p>(5) <a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=rrcuJR6AwVJpb8cKeeeeeFy9Ns9HMRcn4Q0b0b6FVdmaPObVzNImL7o0Lgj6-ekCKeK4Z5MB35WBwZ7vNwiAj6cTjg9sy_PYCL_GCuV75ZHsLXy_7LcIEzceg5gshero6M8CMwHKYiX2-UokNCpRgTZXM' target='_blank'>MPhil/PhD Biological Sciences</a></p><p>(6) <a  href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=6ri8veO7kjzL8RsdNNNNN76K9B6sbzYMe_OvOvBh2efcFXsDjiQVD90rDMa1eBclTBTxcI8gEItgLgFrnZ8sivoJcgfOxuCXUCtzUfniC1aoOZdux0oSVpoErWo1xaYE7rH